      <hr><a name="skip_menu"></a><h1>740 - Added Entry-Uncontrolled Related/Analytical Title (R)</h1>
      <hr>
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Bibliographic - Full</div>
      <div class="datename">October 2003</div>
      <hr>
      <table width="100%">
