         <tr vAlign="top">
            <td colspan="1">$a - Uncontrolled related/analytical title (NR) <br>$h - Medium (NR) <br>$n - Number of part/section of a work (R) <br>$p - Name of part/section of a work (R) <br></td>
            <td colspan="1">$5 - Institution to which field applies (NR) <br>$6 - Linkage (NR) <br>$8 - Field link and sequence number (R) <br></td>
         </tr>
