      <h4><span class="box">&#9632;</span> SUBFIELD CODES
      </h4>
      <div class="subfield"><strong>$a - Uncontrolled related/analytical title</strong> <div class="description">Parenthetical data which may appear as part of the title should not be separately
                              subfield coded.
         </div>
